title: Charlie Ventura - East Of Suez (1945-47) Savoy
description:
CHARLIE VENTURA - EAST OF SUEZ

1. Synthesis (Ventura)
2. Blue Champgne (Watts, Ryerson)
3. Stop'n' Go (Ventura)
4. Soothe Me (Ventura)
5. Pennies From Heaven (Johnston)
6. Eleven-Sixty (Ventura)
7. East Of Suea (Ventura - Stein)
8. Baby, Baby All The Time (unknown)
9. Let's Jump For Rita (Ventura)
10. Out You Go (Ventura)
11. Sweet Georgia Brown (Bernie - Casey - Pinkard)
12. C.V. Jam (Ventura)

1-4:
Charlie Shavers (tp), Bill Harris (tb), Charlie Ventura (ts), Ralph Burns (p), Bill DeArango (g), Chubby Jackson (b), Dave Tough (d), Buddy Stewart (vcl); recorded May, 1947

5-8:
Kai Winding (tb), Charlie Ventura (ts), Lou Stein (p), Bob Carter (b), Shelly Manne (d), Buddy Stewart (vcl); recorded September 11, 1947

9-12:
Buck Clayton (tp), Charlie Ventura (ts), Billy Rowland (p), Ed Yance (g), Al Hall (b), Specs Powell (d); recorded August 1945

2000 Savoy
